title: Sex Shop Prank Calls, Answering DMs & More Instagram Live Hijinks
description:
In case you missed it, Tasia & Camo had some fun going live on Tasia's IG, and now you get to see and hear the whole thing! Camo and Tasia call sex shops asking for wild products, complaining about their orders, as well as taking your suggestions to call YOUR loved ones and scare the hell out of them! Plus, they answer some more of your burning questions, all while being live.

Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube


If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
